## Remarks  
 The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PagerMode> enumeration represents the different display modes for the pager of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataGrid> control. NextPrev displays the pager controls using `Next` and `Previous` buttons; NumericPages displays numeric buttons representing the individual page numbers.  
  
